    "name": "Fight Choreography",
    "prerequisite": "*Acrobat*, or *Gladiator Dedication*; master in Theater Lore",
    "subtype": "feat",
    "text": "You\u2019ve spent enough time training in stage fighting and teaching a wide range of stunts that you can prepare your companions with directions on how to avoid peril in battle. You can Aid an ally\u2019s Acrobatics or Athletics check with a Theater Lore check. You gain the Swift Choreography reaction.  \n  \n**Swift Choreography** (auditory, linguistic)",
